></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">从<strong>0到1</strong>快速上手！</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">快捷跳转微信领取↓↓↓</p>\n<figure class=\"image\" style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://work.weixin.qq.com/ca/cawcde7c151462dece\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://img.jin10.com/news/25/01/x4vFc9m2mA-U5C7L-IY3Q.jpg\"/></a>\n<figcaption style=\"font-size: 12px; margin-top: -16px;\">点此快捷添加客服领取订单流教学</figcaption>\n</figure></div>",
